.TH DAYTIME UCB 2/24/79 UCB
.SH NAME
daytime \- give the time to human-reasonable accuracy
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B daytime
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Daytime
prints out in the English the current time of day,
accurate to the nearest fifteen minutes.  Many people
find this type of abstraction useful, since it doesn't really
matter to them that it's 16:19 when all they wanted to know
is that it's "Quarter past four."
.SH BUGS
.I Daytime
depends on the user to determine whether it's currently night
or day.
